version_description:
Thanks for your continued feedback and support, Bitizens!

What's new:

• Ribbons: try to earn a new one on each life and aim to collect all 23!
• Custom Pets: add your real life pets and watch them randomly show up as characters in your life!
• Over a dozen new dog breeds!
• Kick other animals off your street (if you're the alpha!)
• All-new "strength" attribute
• Tons of bug fixes, life refinements, and new content
• Numerous speed and efficiency improvements

Thanks for your continued feedback and support, Bitizens!
